        <li><strong>Rating:</strong> 4.4/5</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/reviews/titan/" class="text-blue-600 underline">Read full Titan review ‚Üí</a></p>

      <h3>#2: PeterMD ($348/month)</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Customer service + peptides</li>
        <li><strong>Why we ranked it #2:</strong> 4.8/5 Trustpilot rating (highest), same-day doctor replies</li>
        <li><strong>Rating:</strong> 4.8/5 (1,280 reviews)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/reviews/petermd/" class="text-blue-600 underline">Read full PeterMD review ‚Üí</a></p>

