      <ul>
        <li><strong>Best for:</strong> Comprehensive hormone optimization</li>
        <li><strong>Why we ranked it #3:</strong> Testosterone + thyroid + cortisol included, 10k+ reviews</li>
        <li><strong>Rating:</strong> 4.8/5 (10,280 reviews)</li>
      </ul>
