      <h2>Bottom Line: Should You Try Online TRT?</h2>
      <p><strong>Yes, if you:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>‚úÖ Have verified low testosterone (blood test showing &lt;400 ng/dL)</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Experience symptoms (fatigue, low libido, muscle loss)</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Want to save 50-70% vs in-person clinics</li>
        <li>‚úÖ Are comfortable with at-home injections</li>
      </ul>

      <p><strong>Online TRT is not for you if:</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>‚ùå You want someone else to administer injections</li>
        <li>‚ùå You prefer in-person doctor visits</li>
